        <heading>Military voters; prohibiting refusal to accept voter registration and military ballot applications, marked military ballots, and federal ...</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_10_125__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Notarization requirements;\n</p>
